KAME instllation

KAME needs following libraries:
kdelibs and others depending on kdelibs
ruby
gsl
fftw
linux-gpib (optionally)
National Instruments DAQmx library (optionally)
FTGL (must be included in source tree)
mikachanfont (must be included in source tree)

ftgl must be expanded to KAME root source directory.
The document files and the font file of mikachanfont must be copied to (root-source)/kame/mikachanfont

To build FTGL
in directory FTGL/unix
./configure --enable-static --disable-shared
make

To build KAME
./configure (options)
make
make install
